stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Bootstrap

    Bootstrap --> ContextoInicial: install / sdd init
    ContextoInicial --> SistemaMapeado: sdd init-context
    SistemaMapeado --> Onboarding: sdd onboard system

    Onboarding --> Insight: nova ideia
    Insight --> Debate: sdd debate INS-###
    Debate --> Radar: sdd decide --outcome radar
    Debate --> Descartado: sdd decide --outcome discard

    Radar --> Breakdown: sdd breakdown RAD-###
    Breakdown --> FeatReady: FEAT criada e pronta
    Breakdown --> FeatBlocked: FEAT criada mas bloqueada

    FeatBlocked --> FeatReady: dependencias resolvidas
    FeatReady --> EmExecucao: sdd start FEAT-###

    EmExecucao --> ContextoFeat: sdd context FEAT-###
    ContextoFeat --> Implementacao: codar / alterar change / specs

    Implementacao --> Aprovacao: fluxo rigoroso exige gates
    Aprovacao --> ImpactoFrontend: sdd frontend-impact FEAT-###
    Implementacao --> ImpactoFrontend: fluxo direto ou padrao

    ImpactoFrontend --> GapFrontend: frontend requerido sem cobertura
    GapFrontend --> EmExecucao: FGAP aberto e resolvido
    ImpactoFrontend --> ProntaParaArchive: frontend ok ou none justificado

    ProntaParaArchive --> Arquivada: opensdd archive <change>
    Arquivada --> FilaFinalize: aguardando consolidacao
    FilaFinalize --> Finalizada: sdd finalize --ref FEAT-###

    Finalizada --> ADRGerado: ADR + docs + core views
    ADRGerado --> DependentesLiberados: unblock events
    DependentesLiberados --> Onboarding: sistema atualizado

    Descartado --> [*]
    Finalizada --> [*]
